commit.message: Updated build scripts and published new NuGet package.
Added Linq support (with same limitation as HQl support - aggregates don't work)
Fixed aggregation queries using sharded criteria.
Updated NHibernate and NUnit NuGet package dependencies
Build script changes for Sqlite dependencies in tests.

Added ShardedTestCase class

Includes update to NHibernate 4.0.1.
Moved mock classes closer to usage

Merge pull request #1 from rjperes/NHSD-6

NHSD-6
Updated NuGet packages to the latest released versions
Updated build script and tools to support .NET Framework 4
Fixed XML documentation warnings. Removed empty test fixture.
Made NuGet dependency resolution more robust and customisable.
Updated Nuget.exe to 2.0 to solve dependency resolution issues.
Added assembly signing to NAnt build script
Fixed too liberal git ignore patterns that caused trouble for tools directory.
Fixed unit tests execution during build.
Fixed test target in build and added NuGet package publishing target.
Removing lib files that are resolvable via NuGet.
NAnt properties project.version and project.config can now be defined on command line.
Rewrite of build script to add Nuget support.
Added NuGet dependency resolution and package generation.
Fixed race condition when using parallel access strategy.
Optimised SetMaxResults implementation for sharded criteria.

Bug fixes in ISession.Refresh and ISession.Replicate implementation.
Removing obsolete directories.

Removed obsolete IExitOperation interface and its implementations, as they have been merged into single ListExitOperation class.
Resolved various Resharper warnings.

Replaced usage of events in ShardedQueryImpl and SharddedCriteriaImpl by delegates.
Merged IQueryCollector implemntations into exit strategy for List operations. 
Added sharded multiquery and multicriteria implementations.
Added support for futures.
Added ShardedSchemaExport class for efficient creation/dropping of multiple shards from a single NHibernate configuration.
Simplified implementation of ParallelShardAccessStrategy and removed obsolete classes from NHibernate.Shards.Threading namespace.
Implemented missing ICriteria and ISession methods after upgrade to NHibernate v3.0 GA.
Updating NHibernate reference to v3.0 GA
Merging modifications made in https://nhcontrib.svn.sourceforge.net/svnroot/nhcontrib/trunk since branch from Google code repository.
added some methods in ShardedSessionImpl.cs in order to pass the demo application
Preparing to implement parts of the Session

- Parameters of ShardStrategies set to Collection<> instead of IList<>
- Ctor in ShardedConfiguration enabled.

- Schema Export for Demo.
- Relaxing IShardConfiguration.

- ShardStrategyImpl implementing IShardStrategy
- Refactoring in Demo

- Changes to support NH3.
- Example moved to NHibernate.Shards.Demo.
Addedd some Query Api features, some mapping files and /Example and ShardedTableHiLoGenerator.cs
Inherits from Fixture with mocks. Need tests to be passed.
Update Critera features and some Criteria Tests
